        },
        {
            "title": "港股ADR低水163點  長和低水近4%  科網股弱",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港股ADR較恆指周五收市低水163點或0.7%，報23263點。金龍指數跌逾3%，夜期跌146點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"設計圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230927_FI_港股_source-bp_fb.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"設計圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/07/20230927_FI_港股_source-bp_fb.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">設計圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長和(00001) ADR較港收市價低3.9%，折合43.4港元，國家市場監督局反壟斷司展開審查，下周不會就出售巴拿馬港口簽訂協議。 </p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">藥明生物(02269) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低3.3%，折合25.9港元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：藥明生物官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/05/20230823_FI_source-web_02269-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：藥明生物官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股納斯達克跌2.7%，港科網股ADR受壓，攜程(09961) ADR較香港收市價低3.8%，折合487.56元 ; 百度(09888) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低2.7%，折合90.79港元 ;  美團(03690) ADR較香港收市價低1%，折合158.49元。阿里巴巴(09988) ADR較港收市價較港收市價低1.7%，折合128.76港元 ; 騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合港幣505.99元，較香港收市價低0.7% 。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">小米(01810) ADR較香港收市價低1.7%，折合50.17港元 ; 比亞迪(01211) ADR較香港收市價低0.6%，折合404.48港元 ; 理想汽車(02015) ADR較香港收市價低0.3%，折合99.25港元。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"小米SU7 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-ap_China_Xiaomi_SU7.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"小米SU7 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/01/20250102_FI_source-ap_China_Xiaomi_SU7.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">小米SU7 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滙控(00005)ADR折合港元計收報89.87元，較香港收市價高0.5% ; 友邦保險(01299) ADR收市折合港幣59.39元，較香港收市價低0.4% ;  港交所(00388) ADR收市折合港幣349.96元，較香港收市價低1%;  中國平安(02318) ADR收市折合港幣46.75元，較香港收市價低0.4% 。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"集團官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240606_FI_source-web_HSBC_1200-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"集團官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/09/20240606_FI_source-web_HSBC_1200-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">集團官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映中國概念股表現的金龍指數下挫3.11%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">恒指夜市期指收報23284點，跌146點，較昨日恒指收市23426點，低水143點，成交17234張。國指夜市期指收報8553點，較昨日國指收市低水54點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14814400-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1adr%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4163%e9%bb%9e-%e9%95%b7%e5%92%8c%e4%bd%8e%e6%b0%b4%e8%bf%914-%e7%a7%91%e7%b6%b2%e8%82%a1%e5%bc%b1",
