            "title": "油價低收　全周累計連升3星期",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油價轉跌，憂慮美國關稅措施引發全球經濟衰退，但美國加大對委內瑞拉及伊朗施壓，推動油價全周累計連升3星期。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/OILPRICE-1.png.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">紐約期油收報69.36美元，跌56美仙，跌幅0.8%；本周升1.58%。倫敦布蘭特期油收報每桶73.63美元，跌40美仙，跌幅0.54%；本周累計升2.04%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">油田服務商Baker Hughes透露，本周美國油氣井數目減少一個，是三周以來首度下跌。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14814018-%e6%b2%b9%e5%83%b9%e4%bd%8e%e6%94%b6%e3%80%80%e5%85%a8%e5%91%a8%e7%b4%af%e8%a8%88%e9%80%a3%e5%8d%873%e6%98%9f%e6%9c%9f-2",
