            "title": "道指曾插769點納指收跌2.7%　科技七雄指數挫3.5%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美股連續3日低收，道瓊斯工業平均指數周五收挫715點，3大指數跌至近兩星期或以上的低位。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240806_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"美股 (AP圖片)\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1024x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240806_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">美股 (AP圖片)</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">美國上月消費者開支增長不及預期，核心個人消費開支(PCE)物價指數則按月升0.4%，創13個月新高，消費者對未來1年通脹預期升至近兩年半新高。數據加劇市場對通脹升溫及經濟疲弱的擔憂，拖累大市向下，科技股沽壓大。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">道瓊斯工業平均指數低開53點後，跌幅最多擴大至769點，最低報41530點，收市跌幅收窄至715點，收報41583點，全日跌幅約1.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">標普500指數跌穿5600點水平，收報5580點，跌112點，跌幅約2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">納斯達克指數收報17322點，跌481點，跌幅2.7%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">總結全星期，道指累計跌約1%，標普500指數跌1.5%，納指跌2.6%，全部都扭轉前星期升勢。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\"><strong>Alphabet挫半成   Lululemon瀉14.2%</strong></p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科技及汽車股受壓，「科技七雄」指數急滑3.5%，Alphabet挫4.9%，Meta與亞馬遜滑落4.3%，亞馬遜為跌幅最大道指成份股。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">特斯拉(Tesla)股價收市瀉3.5%，輝達(Nvidia)挫1.6%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">通用汽車及福特跌逾1%至近2%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">另外，Lululemon急瀉14.2%，公司下調全年表現預測，受到關稅不確定影響。貿易戰擔憂，推高金價，帶動黃金相關股份表現。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/14814010-%e9%81%93%e6%8c%87%e6%9b%be%e6%8f%92769%e9%bb%9e%e7%b4%8d%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c2-7%e3%80%80%e7%a7%91%e6%8a%80%e4%b8%83%e9%9b%84%e6%8c%87%e6%95%b8%e6%8c%ab3-5",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/08/20240805_FI_source-ap_Financial_Markets_Wall_Street-2-1.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2025-03-29 10:25:51",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
